{"tid":1318540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣彈藥] 當年巴士阿叔(真香港人)既說話真係好撚正 (大量GIF)","createTime":"2019-07-15T03:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T03:57:47.000Z","uid":102343,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c7e80c8eea6fdbf116c27169496b2293be7c3210","tid":1318540,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:11:46.000Z","msg":"阿叔講野好有說服力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推比藍絲睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地應該學阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">左邊:港共政府</span>  <br />\n <span style=\"color: gold;\">右邊:香港人</span><br />\n<br />\n面對不義、出賣香港人既政策同條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQRcFSi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQRcFSi.gif&h=f1f41d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n逼香港人遊行後，林奠話壽終正寢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oUzYBq7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoUzYBq7.gif&h=cd915a76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府沒有誠意的假道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6gwbZ1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6gwbZ1.gif&h=4f5ed4e2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n政府假道歉但係照秋後算帳，不回應5大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OmEE5kv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOmEE5kv.gif&h=579277e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府一日唔滿足我地5大訴求，我地不撤不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1R6cFUE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1R6cFUE.gif&h=9b5dcee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警打9人，政府唔聽人意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，逼到香港人憤怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kOCy9O4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkOCy9O4.gif&h=33acf41f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府一日唔滿足我地5大訴求，我地不撤不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，要逼到政府回應。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GnhCR3u.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGnhCR3u.gif&h=c314eec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港人治港，高度自治。<br />\n你唔搞我地香港，我地理得你咩?<br />\n中共你唔搞我地，比我地真係自治、真普選我地就唔洗動升級啦，成撚日係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V2rgoaU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV2rgoaU.gif&h=432c46b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左邊政府(唔回應增加民怨)+藍絲(話人暴力點知撐警果陣打9人)+CCTVB(假新聞+選擇性報道)<br />\n右邊香港人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Do3bb5W.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDo3bb5W.gif&h=c8a22213&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係政府唔回應5大訴求加黑警打9人先，香港人先diu佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXP2iNt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXP2iNt.gif&h=21f27f47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府+黑警暴行成堆無人問責，唔diu佢diu邊個呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktiq01v.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fktiq01v.gif&h=34158252&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府話想同人對話但佢同時秋後算帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9kNvsG5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9kNvsG5.gif&h=75b31a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你回應5大訴求我地未收手，無謂推前線警察受罪。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/93Z502T.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93Z502T.gif&h=b576cde6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好撚大壓力呀，逼死左幾多人自殺呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人唔撚驚你呀，政府一日唔滿足我地5大訴求，我地不撤不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8XobcaT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8XobcaT.gif&h=05b08026&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25fb47abce136404678dc6692732f3538ca312e9","tid":1318540,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:12:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb57730a9f657113ed7f2dfe80d69100bf2964cb","tid":1318540,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:17:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e46e8ffae8268a0e0731273965967ab356aaf068","tid":1318540,"uid":272458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:18:37.000Z","msg":"高質"},{"pid":"5e6276f9e04de5eebcc0165debd35144e5d40a5b","tid":1318540,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:22:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a0de9a6384882c45f50a36e5276d197b73b9bcd","tid":1318540,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:57:47.000Z","msg":"[文宣-新手教學] 如何得到大量廢老電話號碼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1318650/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1318650/page/1</a>"}]}